title: The Morning After Matthew's Ex Comes to Town
itunes:title: The Morning After Matthew's Ex Comes to Town
description: It's the morning after the Detroit game! Kelly breaks down her weekend and the emotions involved with her best friend, Hank Winchester. The two discuss Lions fans in LA, celebrating after the win, celebrities in their neighborhood, telling the twins apart and much more. There's even a special guest appearance at the top of the show... enjoy!The Morning After podcast is produced by ACTIONPARK MEDIA. Follow us on Social Media:@actionparkmediagroup @kbstafford89@themorningafter.kellystafford
